		<!-- spring-oauth2 -->
		<dependency><!-- spring-security-jwt(2017,2019): spring security jwt is a small utility library for encoding and decoding JSON Web Tokens. It belongs to the family of spring security crypto libraries that handle encoding and decoding text as a general, useful thing to be able to do. -->
